OL,3,CAsylum system delays and backlogs have
OL,4,Cwasted taxpayers' money, watchdog finds
OL,6,FAttempts at short-term fixes to the
OL,7,Fasylum system by the government have
OL,8,Fbrought delays which have wasted
OL,9,Ftaxpayers' money, the public spending
OL,10,Fwatchdog has found.
OL,12,FA report by the National Audit Office
OL,13,F(NAO) found the current cost of
OL,14,Fsupporting people seeking asylum is
OL,15,F"disproportionately high" and totalled
OL,16,Faround #4.9 billion for 2024-25 driven
OL,17,Fby long delays and backlogs.
