OL,3,CAsylum system delays and backlogs have
OL,4,Cwasted taxpayers' money, watchdog finds
OL,6,FThe recommendations come as the
OL,7,Fgovernment announced plans to overhaul
OL,8,Fthe asylum system last month,
OL,9,Fincluding removing its legal duty to
OL,10,Fguarantee support to asylum seekers
OL,11,Fand limiting appeal rights.
OL,13,FBut the NAO said the complex plans
OL,14,Fneed a sustainable approach, or
OL,15,Fotherwise there is a risk of
OL,16,F"unintended consequences for already
OL,17,Fstretched systems".
