OL,3,CAsylum system delays and backlogs have
OL,4,Cwasted taxpayers' money, watchdog finds
OL,6,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,7,F"Successfully implementing the new
OL,8,Fasylum model recently announced by the
OL,9,FHome Secretary will require effective
OL,10,Faction on the bottlenecks in the
OL,11,Fcurrent system using better quality
OL,12,Fdata and streamlined decision-making."
OL,14,FThe NAO's research mapped out the
OL,15,Fasylum system from beginning to end
OL,16,Ffor the first time, which found there
OL,17,Fis no single point of accountability
OL,18,Ffor outcomes throughout the process
OL,19,Facross government.
