OL,3,CAsylum system delays and backlogs have
OL,4,Cwasted taxpayers' money, watchdog finds
OL,6,FThe sample of 5,000 people who first
OL,7,Fmade their initial asylum claim in
OL,8,FJanuary 2023 showed that 35% were
OL,9,Fgranted protection, 9% were removed
OL,10,Ffrom the UK after their claims were
OL,11,Frefused and 56% of the cases remain
OL,12,F"unresolved".
OL,14,FOf the unresolved group, 25% were
OL,15,Fawaiting an appeal decision and 3%
OL,16,Fwere making further submissions.
