OL,3,CAsylum system delays and backlogs have
OL,4,Cwasted taxpayers' money, watchdog finds
OL,6,FSome 4,500 failed asylum seekers were
OL,7,Freceiving support last year, under
OL,8,Fsection four, which can be given while
OL,9,Fthey are making arrangements to leave
OL,10,Fthe UK, when there is another barrier
OL,11,Ffor them to leave the country or they
OL,12,Fare likely to become homeless within
OL,13,F14 days.
OL,15,FThe report said: "Our analysis shows
OL,16,Fhow efforts to improve the system in
OL,17,Frecent years have often been short-
OL,18,Fterm and narrowly focused on one area
OL,19,Fof the system in reaction to large
OL,20,Fbacklogs and sharply increasing costs.
