OL,3,CAsylum system delays and backlogs have
OL,4,Cwasted taxpayers' money, watchdog finds
OL,6,FReacting to the report, Enver Solomon,
OL,7,Fchief executive of the Refugee Council
OL,8,Fcharity, said the government must
OL,9,Ffocus on getting decisions right first
OL,10,Ftime and supporting people to
OL,11,Fintegrate to restore confidence in the
OL,12,Fsystem.
OL,14,F"These findings mirror what we see
OL,15,Fevery day in our frontline services:
OL,16,Fan asylum system that is simply not
OL,17,Ffunctioning, where people wait months
OL,18,For even years for a decision, local
OL,19,Fcouncils are under-resourced and costs
OL,20,Fkeep rising," he said.
